### Get All Pages (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pages

### Get Page by Slug (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pages/slug/terms

### Get Page by ID (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pages/{{pageId}}

### Update Page (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/pages/{{pageId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Terms of Service",
  "content": "<h1>Updated Terms of Service</h1><p>Updated content with new terms and conditions.</p>"
}

### Delete Page (Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/pages/{{pageId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.access_token}} 